File names should follow:

Area(optional)
    NameController

Example:
Admin
    IndexController

Example without Area
SomeController

All method should have documentation example:
/**
* @Post
* @Authorize
* @Admin
* @Route("")
* @param \LoginBindingModel $model
* @throws \Exception
*/

@Authorize, @Admin, @param (for binding models) are required. @Post and @Route
are optional and can be set by config. For more info check Annotations.